The Telegraph - Calcutta

 Perera to replace Zoysa

Colombo: Sri Lanka recalled fast bowler Ruchira Perera in place of the injured Nuwan Zoysa when they named an 18-man squad on Thursday for the tour of New Zealand later this month. 

THE SQUAD 

Maravan Atapattu (captain), Mahela Jayawardene, Sanath Jayasuriya, Kumar Sangakkara, Tillekeratne Dilshan, Thilan Samaraweera, Ian Daniel, Chaminda Vaas, Lasith Malinga, Nuwan Kulasekera, Farveez Maharoof, Upul Chandana, Rangana Herath, Thilina Kandamby, Avishka Gunawardene, Dilhara Fernando, Gayan Wijekoon, Ruchira Perera. (Reuters) 




